# ===== 必填：GitHub 仓库作为数据库 =====
# 创建步骤见 README.md「部署指南」
# GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Fine-grained personal access tokens → Generate new token
# 权限：只选目标仓库，Repository permissions → Contents = Read and write
GH_TOKEN=github_pat_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GH_OWNER=your-github-username
GH_REPO=your-repo-name

# ===== 可选：保护 Cron 触发 =====
# 用于校验 Vercel Cron 来源，避免被恶意触发（部署后在 Vercel 环境变量里也会自动注入）
CRON_SECRET=随便填一串随机字符串
